{"tid":2131182,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前幾日經過上水屠房，見到好多深喉唾液樽一車車咁送入去。。。。。。","createTime":"2020-07-29T16:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:53:36.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00154dfaa7966026f345bde039f6a69624a90252","tid":2131182,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"前幾日經過上水屠房，見到好多深喉唾液樽一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人dum...真係好慘!<br />\n唾液樽係有靈性，幫人檢測....請大家唔好戴口罩! 我都已經開始戒...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202007/29/P2020072900751_photo_1178774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F29%2FP2020072900751_photo_1178774.jpg&h=c4f5cc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">食物環境衞生署（食環署）今日（七月二十九日）表示，鑑於上水屠房近日出現數宗2019冠狀病毒病個案，食環署會為所有進出屠房的持份者（包括營運者、入口商、買手及運輸公司）安排2019冠狀病毒病檢測，務求盡快隔離染病的人員。</span>"},{"pid":"064aee3d0b7b48f707bc54c720e0ad5de8deca87","tid":2131182,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2018/12/facebook_20181206-CR-%E9%A3%9F%E8%A1%9B%E5%B1%805-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2018%2F12%2Ffacebook_20181206-CR-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%25B1%25805-1.jpg&h=01e035e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2179050/org/d669958d2360f9901f7c2af387aa3bae.jpg/HMiAoHd59RdfUkAWXCFxa0j5snSMq-Vwtpevp7aXr6c?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2179050